text: The 1895 Washington Agricultural football team was an American football team that represented Washington Agricultural College during the 1895 college football season. The team competed as an independent under head coach Fred Waite and compiled a record of 2–0, its first undefeated season. ==Schedule== ==References== Washington Agricultural Category:Washington State Cougars football seasons Category:College football undefeated seasons Category:1895 in Washington (state)
